 Dear {!Contact.FirstName}
 
 
To attend the South London BIG Christmas Party, go to www.thechallengesociety.org and log in.  On the home page, click on the event and click the "attend this event" button.  If you don't have your log in details, follow the on-screen instructions, or contact your Challenge Link for help.  

It's going to be a great day, Tuesday 20th December, starting at 10am and finishing at 5pm, involving hosting Christmas parties in elderly care homes, and including a party of your own!!  Ho ho ho!"

See You There



